{"type": "article", "id": 12626, "title": "Moleskine & 哆啦 A 梦 笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-27T07:06:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000215qEQifhG8uF4neOXj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t酷酷的文具品牌 Moleskine 最近和《哆啦 A 梦》联合推出了卡通的笔记本系列，纪念后者 45 周年。这个系列的本子共有四款，每一款都包括两个尺寸的笔记本和两个封面的设计。内页中附赠了大量的插画，并且赠送主题贴纸和书签。这个系列将会在今年 8 月 19 日登陆 Moleskine 官方网站。这是<a href=\"https://store.moleskine.com/hkg/home/index?gclid=CM7_j4S588YCFUhvvAod9mADPw&amp;lang=en-gb\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140333iCF7IhgyQvuMnWpP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66716418\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140334NxqrhQRTFS1dLvbz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140334A19YeIGUKf84o7rz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140335np9W1EYClmxkgyc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}